{"tid":758989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共享單車墳","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T13:38:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61e59905856c136d680e1671b1a5a3ce42120a09","tid":758989,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180728/20462348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F20462348&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3u9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=22f55409\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F20462348&h=2b6ce360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180728/20462348</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月28日 <br />\n<br />\n共享單車墳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180728/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180728%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=10d3e666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■武漢洪山一號，中式亭子淹沒在共享單車的海洋裏，讓這場景獨具「中國特色」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180728/large/a1102b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180728%2Flarge%2Fa1102b.gif&h=9e5ce185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■晨光裏，覆蓋在共享單車上的紗網如雲如霧。<br />\n<br />\n內地自詡共享單車是「新四大發明」，積極拓展海外市場。近月共享單車在海外節節敗退，OFO在一個月內於七個國家撤走或暫停業務，國內在短短兩年已有過百間共享單車公司倒閉，數千萬已投入市場的單車被棄荒野，各城誕生全球獨有的「單車墳墓」。本來提倡環保的共享單車，變成環保的最大敵人。<br />\n<br />\n中國年輕導演、攝影師吳國勇花半年時間，以圖輯「無處安放」為題，走訪各地拍攝單車墳墓，紀錄真實一面。吳表示，廈門的單車墳場最震撼，單車不斷向上堆高至10米，形成真正的「單車牆」。這輯相近日獲得中國當代攝影最重要的獎項之一「映．紀實影像獎」優秀獎和「阿爾帕資助獎」雙重大獎。<br />\n<br />\n新華網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n內地著名戲劇家　揭文革後腐敗　《假如我是真的》原作者病逝<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n失智台商流落四川　舊員工報恩照顧"},{"pid":"00249143881a442502a352b0a1ed3dbab7a65d12","tid":758989,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"環保撚去曬邊"},{"pid":"609fdb8f26016b4f7c340ca89c5de583164fb505","tid":758989,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"一帶一路既野<br />\n你識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747fcc0a2e07029a65056f55661c568cdbdc4ed1","tid":758989,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"內衰"},{"pid":"ce71917a6f0ebeede9d92b5851010f50460b820b","tid":758989,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"2025重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}